name: SuiFloki-Inu
description: What is the project about? SuiFloki Inu is a meme token on SUI Blockchain and the first of its kind to feature a dog breed. Inspired by Dogecoin and Shiba Inu, it has quickly gained popularity online as "the token for dog lovers." It includes a loyalty program that incentivizes long-term holding of the coins. What makes your project unique? SuiFloki Inu is on Sui blockchain which is fairly new and SuiFloki Inu aims to develop a Web3 wallet and staking platform which should drive more adoption of the coin thus attracting more users on Sui blockchain.
